{"tid":706534,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"分享下唔讀書既人吹奏唔讀書既好處","createTime":"2018-06-18T03:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T05:31:12.000Z","uid":100809,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b1ad8aabfc063622543880e72e9080f3c81004e9","tid":706534,"uid":100809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T03:34:03.000Z","msg":"早排有個著名YOUTUBE呢就吹奏唔讀書都好有前途 引起一輪熱話<br />\n咁係佢某條片下面 竟然都出現左個類似既人 仲講左D 我覺得係驚世大膠論既野 咁就純粹分享下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/111915_b54790b884d769399ad1be741db743b7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F18%2F111915_b54790b884d769399ad1be741db743b7.png&h=65da0b97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢位仁兄就吹奏唔讀書+做技術=贏大學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n唔知佢撈邊一門技術咁好搵18歲入行 做到20幾30歲就可以比得起首期 供樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/112616_dffafa273002e825b428c0e6453c6b6e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F18%2F112616_dffafa273002e825b428c0e6453c6b6e.png&h=48d27340&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n做技術點都有3萬4萬 講到咁老定 邊門技術咁好搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n「唔讀書攞緊3-4萬 同一時間 你醫生仲讀緊博士 點同我鬥呀」<br />\n我冇咁叻讀到醫科唔知醫科點運作  但search返黎資料 要讀博士架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似係讀6年+1年實習就得 咁姐係7年 18+7=25歲做醫生  做技術25歲可以賺3-4萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋2018數據醫生起薪5皮幾 比你奇蹟唔讀書做技術25歲搵3-4萬 都睇唔出點贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4767d8a4ebc5cfcc4b02295d1a946df582e16845","tid":706534,"uid":100809,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T03:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/114153_6466136d1077a4900f42c47e312d4188.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F18%2F114153_6466136d1077a4900f42c47e312d4188.png&h=c502e7a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「讀醫科讀律師唔係攞大學學位去面試」 姐係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有大學學位 但又去用大學學位面試讀另一個大學學位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大學仔諗以後自己會搵3-4萬既時候 洗碗/做技術已經袋緊1萬蚊= 唔讀書好過讀書? 唔明咩思路<br />\n同埋現實應該係「大學生諗以後會搵3-4萬既時候 而家袋緊2萬幾 洗碗/做技術就袋得1萬幾」<br />\n<br />\n洗碗/技術去進修贏大學生 會唔會太離地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢吹奏唔讀書都可以贏大學生 但又話洗碗/技術會去進修 姐係點?精神分裂? 定係特登唔進修大學學位 進修個HD? 完全諗唔明"},{"pid":"3721ae7fee3a78139f2fab9da009de28e414cca2","tid":706534,"uid":156592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T05:07:02.000Z","msg":"講到底未因為條友自己讀唔成書囉"},{"pid":"6e2a21561a3a3d29de50dfd768717a1f46976ad5","tid":706534,"uid":100809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3721ae7fee3a78139f2fab9da009de28e414cca2","tid":706534,"uid":156592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T05:07:02.000Z","msg":"講到底未因為條友自己讀唔成書囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T05:31:12.000Z","msg":"撐唔係問題 你咪避重就輕囉 都可以水到D邏輯唔清晰既人<br />\n但佢D point係完全冇邏輯冇常識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}